  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate that IMT associated with a conventional pulmonary rehabilitation program allows a
      significant improvement of dyspnea in subjects with severe or very severe COPD than a
      conventional pulmonary rehabilitation program alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
